When we upgraded to 3.2 one of my users complained that he was unable to edit the name of a screenshot before attaching it. Before 3.2, he could go to More > Attach screenshot and then at the bottom of the form was a file name that you could edit. Now, that form has changed (maybe because of introduction of WYSIWYG?) and you can no longer change the file name. This request is to allow that ability. I have included screenshots of both the 3.0 Service Desk attachment form and the 3.2 attachment form.

